NOTE ON FIRMWARE FILES:

The firmware files referenced in this project (BT_RAM_CODE_MT7902_1_1_hdr.bin
and mtkbt0.dat) are proprietary and copyrighted by MediaTek Inc.

This repository does NOT include or distribute these firmware files. Users must
obtain firmware files from their own Windows installations or other legal sources.

The scripts and documentation in this repository are provided to facilitate the
use of legally-obtained firmware files with Linux systems.
